{"id": 2451, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于参加同学聚会这个事，你都有过哪些心得 or 教训？", "description": "怎么比当年上学还累呢？（题图来自：iStock © chihhang）", "record_count": 3051, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180704235146lqmcunjSe2Y1Xkd5.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-30T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 295680, "content": "能推就推，还是跟聊得来的老同学小聚比较有意义。", "image": null, "praise_count": 194, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116698}, {"id": 295936, "content": "见了不该见的人又感觉尴尬了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421938}, {"id": 295682, "content": "我的同学聚会很愉快啊，谈一谈自己的工作经历，并不觉得是比收入。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327163}, {"id": 295938, "content": "找到自己热爱的事情，并坚持下去做，但前提是保证能维持家庭的正常生存。\n\n是很难的，需要不断的学习和反思。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417103}, {"id": 295683, "content": "只跟比较熟的同学去聚会，至于不熟的会想办法推掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420597}, {"id": 297219, "content": "不熟的人还是不熟，无话可说的人还是无话可说，总体看这种聚会没有任何必要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 295684, "content": "初中注册qq，那时就从来不加同学。各种校友人人也没注册过，现在发现我的做法实在是太对了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420608}, {"id": 295940, "content": "不去不去不爱去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190085}, {"id": 295685, "content": "忆苦思甜？不存在的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420628}, {"id": 295941, "content": "无聊的说", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421982}, {"id": 295686, "content": "别去", "image": null, "praise_count": 331, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 386839}, {"id": 295942, "content": "没有同学会的同学路过～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376759}, {"id": 295687, "content": "能不去最好别去，私下再跟要好的再聚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275828}, {"id": 295943, "content": "聚会也许只适合第一次去，再多了就变成无聊和没话找话了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191706}, {"id": 295688, "content": "小聚怡情，大聚烧身", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270343}, {"id": 295689, "content": "尽量嘴上装穷细节不装穷，给人一种装穷的错觉，最后你怎么说穷都没人会信你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275828}, {"id": 296457, "content": "吃不到想吃的饭，说不上想说的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424219}, {"id": 295690, "content": "去的都是些混得比较好的不是吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420642}, {"id": 295692, "content": "只是想看看昔日的同窗们怎么样了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399537}, {"id": 296204, "content": "会觉得再见已是陌生人，有人感慨过去有人却无所谓", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423073}, {"id": 296716, "content": "一定提后悔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423837}, {"id": 295693, "content": "为了咱美好的幼时回忆，还是能不去则不去了吧...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 295694, "content": "别去就完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420653}, {"id": 295950, "content": "懒得去，因为不想见到前男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422088}, {"id": 295695, "content": "从不去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928472}, {"id": 295951, "content": "衣服上:一个比一个穿的好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422091}, {"id": 295697, "content": "聚会本来是给老同学回忆学生往事的，但现在各种炫富攀比，早就把聚会搞得乌烟瘴气。现在，更喜欢小范围的同学聚会，想见的随时都可以见，不需要大张旗鼓搞个大型聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843527}, {"id": 295953, "content": "换个说法即若干小团体到同一个地方玩着手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416809}, {"id": 295954, "content": "就一概别去就行了，想见谁私下约出来更好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341302}, {"id": 295699, "content": "期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420682}, {"id": 295955, "content": "如果没有经常联系的熟人，同学聚会我只是当做一天垃圾信息，一看就忘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414988}, {"id": 297235, "content": "混得不好就不要去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428294}, {"id": 295700, "content": "闹心还没意义的聚会，去了干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354542}, {"id": 295701, "content": "绝对不要惹人生气，因为这会毁掉整个聚会", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420677}, {"id": 295957, "content": "混不在一起的人，终究不会混在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 295702, "content": "同学会…应该十周年才有可能聚一次吧，毕业三年了班级群没有一个人说话?再过十年不见我也不想去，没什么意义。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278548}, {"id": 298006, "content": "不去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431999}, {"id": 295703, "content": "敬酒前多吃点菜，高中同学聚会有几个傻孩子一来就灌了两瓶老白干，以至于发展到后来一桌人没怎么吃菜，喝了十几瓶江小白，最后有两个同学酒精中毒送医院差点出人命，把我们这些组织者吓个半死，以后都不想组织同学聚会了。那些不能喝的同学们，身体第一，面子在生命面前都是浮云。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022408}, {"id": 296471, "content": "太虚荣   感情建立在有钱的基础上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424179}, {"id": 295709, "content": "不去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294836}, {"id": 295710, "content": "因为没有什么特别要好的人，感觉大家都在抱团叙旧自己一个人站着很尴尬，所以至今没参加过任何聚会....", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334247}, {"id": 295711, "content": "做一个低调的大佬，别去和别人攀比。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262462}, {"id": 296223, "content": "除了尴尬，就是发现从前谈得来的人，现在与自己的价值观完全不一样了，无法沟通交流！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082191}, {"id": 295712, "content": "贼无聊。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419166}, {"id": 295713, "content": "看到前男友/女友，会很尴尬吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395205}, {"id": 295714, "content": "同学聚会，还是经常聚的那波人聊的多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406218}, {"id": 295715, "content": "从不参加", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394550}, {"id": 296227, "content": "感觉都有些陌生了。可能圈子早就不同了。", "image": "img/option/option/20180801003405ocp0Q7TVqj9ELDHU", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422040}, {"id": 295716, "content": "聚会见面，千篇一律，同学们渐行渐远，生疏又陌生，物是人非。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412612}, {"id": 296231, "content": "工作太忙去不了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423163}]}